    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Pristine & Move-In Ready \u2014 A Genuine Mint Condition Gem! This car is the real deal \u2014 mint condition from bumper to bumper, and it absolutely shows. The exterior shines with no visible scratches, dents, or blemishes, while the interior is fresh, clean, and well-preserved with no signs of significant wear. Mechanically, this vehicle has been well cared for and is ready to hit the road without any concerns. If you're looking for a used car that feels as close to new as it gets, this is your opportunity \u2014 don't let it pass you by!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Mint condition gem available now! This vehicle is in absolutely pristine shape \u2014 the paint is flawless, the interior looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor, and every system runs with precision and confidence. Whether you're cruising on the highway or pulling into the office, this car delivers a driving experience that feels brand new. Don't miss your chance to own a truly exceptional vehicle that's been kept in outstanding condition from day one!",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 **Budget-Friendly & Priced to Reflect Reality \u2014 A Project Car Opportunity!** We're being straight with you on this one: this vehicle is in poor condition and priced accordingly! It has seen better days \u2014 expect visible wear and cosmetic issues on the exterior, a worn interior, and some mechanical attention needed before it's running at its best. That said, it does get you from point A to point B, making it a potential fit for a handy buyer, a first project car, or someone who needs basic transportation on a tight budget. No surprises here \u2014 what you see is what you get, and the price reflects every bit of that honesty. Come take a look and decide for yourself!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition \u2014 a well-maintained, reliable car that has been thoughtfully cared for and is ready for everyday driving. The exterior presents nicely, with the paint retaining a good shine and only minor surface blemishes consistent with normal use \u2014 no significant dents, deep scratches, or rust to report. The interior is clean and comfortable, with upholstery showing light wear on high-contact areas but no tears, stains, or damage worth noting. All major mechanical systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and suspension \u2014 are in solid working order, and the car starts and drives confidently. You can expect a dependable vehicle that doesn't require immediate repairs, though as with any used car, routine maintenance should be kept up. A great option for a buyer looking for solid value without the premium of a mint-condition vehicle.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition \u2014 a practical choice for buyers seeking reliable transportation at an accessible price point. The car starts and runs, making it a dependable daily driver, but buyers should be aware that it shows its age and use. The exterior has noticeable scratches, scuffs, and paint fade in several areas, and there may be minor dents or dings consistent with everyday wear. The interior is functional but worn \u2014 expect faded upholstery, some surface scratches on trim pieces, and general signs of regular use. Mechanically, the car gets you where you need to go, though it may benefit from some routine maintenance or minor repairs in the near future. This is an honest, no-frills used car priced to reflect its actual condition \u2014 ideal for a buyer who values utility over cosmetics.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $5,500, a price that honestly reflects its poor condition \u2014 and we want to be fully transparent about what that means before you consider purchasing. This car has significant issues that a buyer should be fully aware of. The exterior shows considerable wear including rust, dents, and damaged paint in multiple areas. The interior is worn and has damage to seating, trim, and likely the headliner. Mechanically, this vehicle has known problems and should be expected to require substantial repairs before it can be relied upon for regular use. It may not pass a basic inspection in its current state. This listing is best suited for a buyer who is comfortable with a major project vehicle, someone looking for parts, or a buyer with mechanical expertise who can assess and address the issues themselves. We strongly recommend a thorough pre-purchase inspection by a qualified mechanic before committing to this purchase. There are no warranties implied or offered at this price point.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    }
